nnoremap <space>ga :Git add .<CR><CR>
nnoremap <space>gst :G<CR>
nnoremap <space>gd :Gdiff<CR>
nnoremap <space>gco :Git checkout
nnoremap <space>gcm :Git checkout main<CR>
nnoremap <space>grb :Git rebase
nnoremap <space>grbm :Git rebase main<CR>
nnoremap <space>gcc :Git rebase -continue<CR>
nnoremap <space>gsta :Git stash
nnoremap <space>gstp :Git stash pop<CR>
nnoremap <space>gl :Git pull<CR>
nnoremap <space>gp :Git push<CR>
nnoremap <space>gpf :Git push --force-with-lease<CR>



